metadata.name: BOYS DO CRY, Amsterdam 2019
metadata.description:
This is one of the photos from the book.

Learn more about the project: www.prinsdevos.com/boys-do-cry

First buyers will receive a physical copy of the photo book + a limited edition print. Ebook available at Opensea.

The book launch took place on May 2022, presented by Amsterdam Museum, OBA, Transgender Netwerk & IHLIA-LGBT Heritage.
